snippet.title: Wrongworld Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Wrongworld officially launches on Friday the 11th of May!

But just because it's time to leave early access, that doesn't mean this is the end of development - far from it! This is just the beginning...

Steam: http://store.steampowered.com/app/664750/Wrongworld/
Twitter: https://twitter.com/SludjGames
Discord: https://discord.gg/FYP9Xht

About Wrongworld
Crash-landed on a surreal, low-poly world filled with freakish inhabitants, choose between permadeath and non-permadeath modes and embark on an epic (and ridiculous) survival adventure. Will you manage to stay alive as you unravel the mysteries of Wrongworld and search for a way home?
